Avid (company)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Avid Technology)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the technology and multimedia company. For the educational program, see Advancement Via Individual Determination. For other uses, see AVID (disambiguation).





